                  </hi>. I am the wife of Thomas Lefcester, of Pereival-street, Clerkenwell. On 2nd April, I paid the prisoner 10 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for bread from Mr. Watson.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
